    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s been well-loved, well-maintained, and honestly still looks great out on the road! It runs like a dream and is totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that won't let you down, you've found it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
