    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2011 Porsche Cayman S (987.2), a definitive example of mid-engine equilibrium. This specimen features the 3.4L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear 320 hp and 273 lb-ft of torque through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The 987.2 generation is highly sought after for its revised engine architecture, which eliminated the IMS bearing concerns of its predecessors. The chassis maintains factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by a well-sorted MacPherson strut suspension and communicative hydraulic power steering. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive borescope inspection and a fresh set of high-performance tires. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight, the limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit bite, and the throttle response is telepathic. A purist\u2019s tool designed for technical apex hunting.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
