      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV offers the perfect balance of performance and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy metallic finish, though it shows minor, typical road wear on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and the interior has been kept strictly smoke-free. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health, having recently passed a full multi-point inspection. It features a brand-new set of all-season tires and has just undergone a synthetic oil service. Every electronic component\u2014from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. I have retained all service records to demonstrate a history of preventative care. This is a dependable, high-end vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 36500.0,
